info.name: FurAffinity - Monochrome Notification Icons
info.description:
A set of one-tone color coded icons for furaffinity.net's navigation bar. One for Submissions (Blue Hanging Canvas), Comments/Journals/Favorites/Watches (Green Word Bubble), Note (Yellow Note with Pen), Trouble Ticket (Red Bug).

Made by me. (Cheezy WEAPON)
info.additionalInfo:
*Works best with DARK themes!*

Looks best with KISS Lite Theme (Also by me) here-
http://userstyles.org/styles/71818/furaffinity-kiss-lite-theme

If anything breaks or looks wrong, let me know!
Icons are in data url format.
